{"type": "article", "id": 16044, "title": "折叠桌", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-14T07:08:46Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 60, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702135547S29hk3HWGQXlPw7T.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这张折叠桌可以像折纸一样翻来翻去，圆形桌板上有几条折线，沿着边缘轻轻掀开，桌子就像花朵一样展开了。当桌面收缩成一小块时，桌腿也能并在一起，成为一个小凳子。来自瑞典的设计师称，灵感源于翻折地图时折皱感，而从圆桌变成凳子的过程也像一场魔术，非常好玩。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143430nKPvuds5mrXctw6G.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"640\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143430eRUqZpVvF5chIL6o.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"640\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143431wibIoxfD9YglzZJc.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"640\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}